uid":158806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"茶記的啊叔啊嬸根本就係新移民藍絲多<br />\n又日日睇住cctvb十個八個鐘，入晒腦<br />\n著黑衫既都唔知食左幾多廚師白汁同啊嬸西酉汁"},{"pid":"b801b864aed6fab1ff1923a4c6dc150f6355643a","tid":1529754,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>葵涌警署16輔警年卅食「泰星匯」海南雞飯疑食物中毒 衛生署調查<br />\n</strong><br />\n衛生防護中心今日（8日）公布一宗疑食物中毒，葵涌警署16人在年三十晚（4日）進食區內泰國餐廳「泰星匯泰國菜」的海南雞飯加辣醬後，陸續內出現腹瀉、腹痛、噁心、嘔吐和發燒等病徵。其中7人曾經求醫，一人入住浸會醫院，經治療後已出院；他們全部情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，16人為輔警，他們於當晚上進食有關飯盒後，出現腹痛及腹瀉等病徵。警務處會配合相關部門調查有關案件。"},{"pid":"668f725b6d9a688adcd53e481d39dbcc53b2b3bb","tid":1529754,"uid":801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cbb7fd8bc0fbe2f778d7b26c0f2787dc22d673","tid":1529754,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"仲有用著過嘅絲襪沖奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d19e390f9fa12bcd053d609c7dd2b63434ac3e7","tid":1529754,"uid":801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b70bcf35c8f5f97d52ca1d3673d1db4a05c8eb6","tid":1529754,"uid":801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"凍撚水計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7a66e7d3fd663f18b6ba99562dd262fbc34266","tid":1529754,"uid":308152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117f9e10cb7fbda49ea115641730562249c115d3","tid":1529754,"uid":801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:40:10.000Z","msg":"等警犬安心黎食飯<br />\n然後就大大啖飲你精心泡製既凍撚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-0